title: Taiwan, US Sign Trade Pact
description: The US and Taiwan finalized a trade agreement to cut tariffs, boost market access for American products in Asia and channel billions of dollars into US energy and technology projects. Bloomberg's Laura Davison reports. (Source: Bloomberg)
